data.description: This beautiful 2550 square foot 4 bedroom 2 and a half bath home sits toward the end of a cul-de-sac on a spacious lot! This is an opportunity you won't want to pass up! This home's potential is endless with its vast amounts of functional living space and layout. Enjoy the open floorplan which features a connected living room, dining room and kitchen that allow for great family time while cooking or just sitting around visiting with family and friends. All kitchen appliances will convey with the (exception of the refrigerator). Privacy is intended with the main bedroom with its own bathroom and walk in closet located on the first floor and all other bedrooms are on the second floor! There is a huge landing area that can serve as an office, playroom, additional living room, or any flex space desired. There is a spacious fence back yard with a covered porch and an inground irrigation system to help maintain the already established yard. This home is ready for its new owners, so come see what this home can offer you today!
